#: ../source/tutorial/convert-shard-standalone-to-shard-replica-set.txt:8
msgid "Starting in MongoDB 3.6, all shards must be replica sets. Before you can upgrade your 3.4 sharded cluster to version 3.6, you must convert any shards that are running as standalone :binary:`~bin.mongod` instances to replica set shards."
msgstr ""

