msgid "This tutorial describes the process for converting a shard standalone into a shard :term:`replica set`. The procedure is specific to a shard standalone. To convert just a standalone to a replica set (i.e. not a part of any sharded cluster), see :doc:`/tutorial/convert-standalone-to-replica-set` instead."
msgstr ""

